## form requests

# NOT RUN {
(cli <- HttpClient$new(
  url = "http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/advsearch.do"
))
cli$post(
  encode = "form",
  body = list(
    page = 'advancedSearch',
    genus = 'Gagea',
    species = 'pratensis',
    selectedLevel = 'cont'
  )
)
# }
